# Portfolio Build — Full Task Checklist

## Phase 0 — Init & Setup
- [ ] Check existing project folder, clean if needed
- [ ] Init Next.js 14 App Router + TypeScript project
- [ ] Install all dependencies (Tailwind, R3F, Drei, Framer Motion)
- [ ] Configure tailwind.config.ts (colors, fonts, spacing tokens)
- [ ] Configure tsconfig, next.config.ts
- [ ] Set up global CSS (design tokens, scrollbar, selection)
- [ ] Set up Google Fonts via next/font (Inter, Cal Sans)
- [ ] Create folder structure: components/, sections/, lib/, types/, public/

## Phase 1 — Layout Shell
- [ ] Root layout.tsx: metadata, fonts, body wrapper
- [ ] Navbar: sticky, blur, logo, nav links, CTA button
- [ ] Footer: links, copyright, socials
- [ ] Page wrapper with smooth scroll

## Phase 2 — Hero Section
- [ ] Hero layout: name, title, tagline, CTAs
- [ ] Framer Motion: staggered text fade-in
- [ ] R3F 3D scene: floating geometric mesh + ambient particles
- [ ] GPU detection + mobile fallback (static gradient)
- [ ] Scroll-down indicator animation

## Phase 3 — What I Do Section
- [ ] 3 service cards (Mobile, Web, Backend)
- [ ] Hover glow + border animation
